      "file_path": "kubernetes/a1policymanagementservice/resources/config/application_configuration.json",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 14,
      "message": "a1-sim is not a namespace.\nThe A1 simulator will be deployed as a statefulset. to access the specific ric, <statefulsetname-instance.service>.\n\nIt is a delivered as part of ORAN/OSC bronze (Not a ONAP delivery) release and it is mentioned here just as an example. Now I have removed this in patchset 6 to avoid confusion. 😊",
